column16: Travis d'Arnaud flies out to left fielder Derek Dietrich.

Curtis Granderson singles on a line drive to left fielder Derek Dietrich.   Kelly Johnson scores.    Michael Conforto scores.    Bartolo Colon to 2nd.
Bartolo Colon singles on a ground ball to center fielder Christian Yelich.   Kelly Johnson to 3rd.    Michael Conforto to 2nd.
Michael Conforto singles on a line drive to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.   Kelly Johnson to 2nd.
Travis d'Arnaud flies out to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
Will Venable grounds out, pitcher Chris Reed to first baseman Casey McGehee.
Clint Barmes pops out to third baseman Martin Prado in foul territory.
Alexi Amarista out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Chris Reed to first baseman Casey McGehee.   Andrew Cashner to 2nd.
Jedd Gyorko singles on a line drive to center fielder Christian Yelich.
